01:44:05,140 --> 01:44:09,160
就好像我在和你们
as if I were able to cross your threshold...

1431
01:44:10,320 --> 01:44:13,810
面对面交谈
and speak to you myself.

1432
01:44:18,200 --> 01:44:22,140
对我们大多数人来说  有生之年
For the second time in the lives of most of us,

1433
01:44:23,130 --> 01:44:27,670
我们再一次面临  面临战争
we are at... at war.

1434
01:44:32,170 --> 01:44:36,140
一次有一次
Over and over again,

1435
01:44:37,620 --> 01:44:40,460
我们竭尽全力
we have tried to find...

1436
01:44:43,100 --> 01:44:51,130
想为我们和那些如今成为敌人的人之间的差异
a peaceful way out of the differences between ourselves...

1437
01:44:52,550 --> 01:45:00,180
找到和平的解决办法
and those who are now our enemies.

1438
01:45:02,220 --> 01:45:05,410
但终是突然
But it has been in vain.

1439
01:45:07,600 --> 01:45:11,000
我们被迫面临冲突
We have been forced into a conflict.

1440
01:45:12,370 --> 01:45:17,040
因为我们是被号召去挑战一种信条
For we are called, to meet the challenge of a principle

1441
01:45:18,420 --> 01:45:20,680
这种信条如果获胜
which, if it were to prevail,

1442
01:45:21,400 --> 01:45:25,000
将是对全世界文明秩序的
would be fatal to any civilized order...

1443
01:45:26,430 --> 01:45:27,680
致命打击
in the world.

1444
01:45:29,110 --> 01:45:30,870
这种信条
Such a principle,

1445
01:45:32,190 --> 01:45:36,200
剥除所有伪装
stripped of all disguise,

1446
01:45:37,650 --> 01:45:40,240
无疑是一种简单的
is surely the mere...

1447
01:45:44,130 --> 01:45:50,130
原始信条  那就是强权即真理
primitive doctrine that might is right.

1448
01:45:52,130 --> 01:45:56,890
为了我们所珍惜的一切
For the sake of all that we ourselves hold dear,

1449
01:45:58,020 --> 01:46:08,100
毫无疑问  我们不应拒绝迎接这种挑战
it is unthinkable that we should refuse to meet the challenge.

1450
01:46:11,000 --> 01:46:18,270
为了这个崇高的目标  在此
It is to this high purpose that I now call...

1451
01:46:18,990 --> 01:46:26,100
我号召海内外所有的大英臣民
my people at home and my peoples across the seas,

1452
01:46:26,850 --> 01:46:31,470
将我们事业当作自己的事业
who will make our cause their own.

1453
01:46:32,220 --> 01:46:38,010
请你们保持镇静和坚定
I ask them to stand calm and firm,

1454
01:46:39,110 --> 01:46:43,020
在此危难之时团结一致
and united in this time of trial.

1455
01:46:44,150 --> 01:46:46,450
任务十分艰巨
The task will be hard.

1456
01:46:47,890 --> 01:46:51,440
我们前方也许是黑暗
There may be dark days ahead,

1457
01:46:51,980 --> 01:46:59,250
