But we can only do the right as we see the right...

1459
01:47:06,010 --> 01:47:13,950
并向上帝虔诚祈祷
and reverently commit our cause to God.

1460
01:47:16,380 --> 01:47:23,950
如果我们所有人都能坚定信念
If one and all we keep resolutely faithful to it,

1461
01:47:25,200 --> 01:47:29,150
那么  有上帝的庇佑
then, with God's help,

1462
01:47:31,150 --> 01:47:34,760
我们将取得胜利
we shall prevail.

1463
01:47:50,200 --> 01:47:51,700
非常好  博迪
Very good, Bertie.

1464
01:48:06,640 --> 01:48:09,060
你说"和"还是有点结巴
You still stammered on the "w"?

1465
01:48:10,430 --> 01:48:13,810
总得结巴几下  他们才知道是我
Had to throw in a few so they knew it was me.

1466
01:48:19,150 --> 01:48:22,200
恭喜您  国王陛下  一次真正的广播
