1474
01:49:03,390 --> 01:49:04,890
谢谢你  罗格
Thank you, Logue.

1475
01:49:14,390 --> 01:49:17,830
干得好  我的朋友
Well done, my friend.

1476
01:49:20,520 --> 01:49:23,810
谢谢您  国王陛下
Thank you, Your Majesty.

1477
01:49:36,820 --> 01:49:38,470
我知道你行的
I knew you'd be good.

1478
01:49:47,830 --> 01:49:50,470
谢谢你  莱昂纳尔
Thank you, Lionel.

1479
01:49:54,150 --> 01:49:55,650
